family:\" times=\"\"><o:p></o:p></span></strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<strong style=\"color: rgb(105, 105, 105); font-family: Arial; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial; color: gray;\">Une fois le dossier complet envoy&eacute;, il sera &eacute;tudi&eacute; sous 72 heures ouvr&eacute;es. </span></span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:Arial;color:gray;mso-themecolor:background1;\r\nmso-themeshade:128\"><o:p></o:p></span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<strong style=\"color: rgb(105, 105, 105); font-family: Arial; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><b><span style=\"font-family: Arial; color: rgb(178, 0, 102);\">Le dossier doit &ecirc;tre envoy&eacute; complet et mis en ligne au plus tard le 31 ao&ucirc;t 2015. Il devra avoir &eacute;t&eacute; accept&eacute; par notre comit&eacute; risque, financ&eacute; par la communaut&eacute; et d&eacute;caiss&eacute; par l&rsquo;emprunteur.</span></b><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"> </span></span><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Arial;\"><o:p></o:p></span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<strong style=\"color: rgb(105, 105, 105); font-family: Arial; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><br />\r\n	<b>Une question&nbsp;? &nbsp;</b></span></span><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Arial;\"><b><o:p></o:p></b></span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<strong style=\"color: rgb(105, 105, 105); font-family: Arial; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><b><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">Contactez-nous au </span></b><b><span style=\"font-family:Arial;color:#B20066;border:none windowtext 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:\r\nnone windowtext 0cm;padding:0cm\">01 82 83 66 55</span></b><b><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"> ou par mail &agrave; l&#39;adresse </span></b><b><span style=\"font-family:Arial;color:#B20066;\r\nborder:none windowte